《'''漫画中国成语'''》是[[敖幼祥|敖幼祥]]的漫画，全套六册<ref name="時報悅讀網">{{Cite news|url=http://www.readingtimes.com.tw/ReadingTimes/ProductPage.aspx?gp=productdetail&cid=mcic(SellItems)&id=FT0863Y|title=漫畫中國成語全套(共6冊)(FT0863Y)|language=zh-tw|publisher=時報悅讀網|author=|date=|accessdate=2015-02-03|archive-date=2016-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306004417/http://www.readingtimes.com.tw/ReadingTimes/ProductPage.aspx?gp=productdetail&cid=mcic(SellItems)&id=FT0863Y|dead-url=no}}</ref>，書中將[[成語|成語]]画成漫畫情節来介绍成语，于1993年由[[時報文化|時報文化]]先陸續推出<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.readingtimes.com.tw/ReadingTimes/ProductPage.aspx?gp=productdetail&cid=rtfa%28SellItems%29&id=FA0076|title=漫畫中國成語(一)(FA0076)|language=zh-tw|publisher=時報悅讀網|author=|date=|accessdate=2015-02-03|archive-date=2021-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123011715/http://www.readingtimes.com.tw/ReadingTimes/ProductPage.aspx?gp=productdetail&cid=rtfa(SellItems)&id=FA0076|dead-url=no}}</ref>，由《[[乌龙院|乌龙院]]》的师徒等人物诠释[[成语|成语]]故事<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://cartoon.southcn.com/a/ycll/content/2013-04/15/content_67049323.htm|title=漫画家敖幼祥：画漫画 文是第一|language=zh-cn|publisher=《羊城晚报》|author=|date=2013-04-15|accessdate=2015-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150120040841/http://cartoon.southcn.com/a/ycll/content/2013-04/15/content_67049323.htm|archive-date=2015-01-20|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。簡體中文版于2002年10月由[[漓江出版社|漓江出版社]]出版<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.ycwb.com/gb/content/2002-10/22/content_439358.htm|title=一套适合各年龄层阅读的漫画书|language=zh-cn|publisher=金羊网|author=|date=2013-04-15|accessdate=2015-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150211084747/http://www.ycwb.com/gb/content/2002-10/22/content_439358.htm|archive-date=2015-02-11|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。荣获[[国立编译馆优良漫画奖|国立编译馆优良漫画奖]]三次。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.southcn.com/cartoon/gzparty2006/jnhxx/200512170001.htm|title=2006年2月广州漫展：台湾漫画大师敖幼祥将出席嘉年华|language=zh-cn|publisher=南方动漫网|author=|date=2013-04-15|accessdate=2015-02-03|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304221918/http://www.southcn.com/cartoon/gzparty2006/jnhxx/200512170001.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

